{"tid":1706950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文：政府不該對手無寸鐵的人民開槍 開槍只會惡化問題","createTime":"2019-11-11T08:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T08:07:56.000Z","uid":10338,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1a7395d749d0754978e2c072f7bfc75f6d61f7ff","tid":1706950,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:01:34.000Z","msg":"政府不該對手無寸鐵的人民開槍，開槍只會惡化問題。<br />\n　　<br />\n北京和港府該回應香港人民的，不是子彈，而是對民主自由的承諾。<br />\n　　<br />\n這段時間發生在香港的事件，讓人非常遺憾。我要再次呼籲香港政府，對話才能解決問題，認真看待香港人民對自由民主的渴望並具體回應，才是回復穩定與秩序的唯一道路。<br />\n　　<br />\n我衷心期盼，台灣對民主自由的堅持，能成為香港的座標。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1yr5P3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1yr5P3.png&h=240cc029&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1848bc6ad38fe614557e55a95e0bcaaf57619a4","tid":1706950,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:02:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b036534f97c9525a54ac2c29d2bd346aafeec91f","tid":1706950,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:03:09.000Z","msg":"台灣選左蔡英文上去<br />\n<br />\n等變香港啦"},{"pid":"126adafeec241a5110f48bd653e788dacce907ad","tid":1706950,"uid":131084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:03:53.000Z","msg":"Noted with thanks<br />\n出多幾篇Facebook status就可以幫到香港架啦"},{"pid":"3b79125ff4e65485e8c8fe06b917e369f9ad3832","tid":1706950,"uid":62714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b036534f97c9525a54ac2c29d2bd346aafeec91f","tid":1706950,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:03:09.000Z","msg":"台灣選左蔡英文上去<br />\n<br />\n等變香港啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"你講韓國魚啊？<br />\n五毛拉"},{"pid":"4c35d123bb13e11c31f7fd54b23e2bf59f95b8ab","tid":1706950,"uid":323443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"126adafeec241a5110f48bd653e788dacce907ad","tid":1706950,"uid":131084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-1